---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const STRIPE_CHECKOUT_URL = "/api/checkout/session?dataset=finma";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="FINMA Registry Unified — Swiss Compliance Dataset | openswissdata"
  description="All 10 FINMA authorised-institutions lists unified under one schema. Banks, insurance, PSPs, asset managers, SRO members, and more. 299 CHF one-shot."
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <nav class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">
      <a href="/" class="hover:underline">Home</a> · <a href="/bundle" class="hover:underline">All datasets</a> · <span>FINMA Registry</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between flex-wrap gap-4 mb-2">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">FINMA Registry Unified</h1>
      <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-600">CHF 299</div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">
      10 FINMA-authorised-institutions lists unified under one schema. Banks, insurance companies, PSPs/fintechs, asset managers (collective + individual), securities firms, fund representatives, SRO members, supervisory organisations, insurance intermediaries. UID + LEI enriched. Weekly delta updates.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10 text-sm">
      <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="font-semibold mb-1 text-slate-900">Formats included</div>
        <div class="text-slate-600">CSV (unified + per-type) · JSON · Parquet · SQL · 90-day changelog · JSON Schema · README · LICENSE · SHA-256</div>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="font-semibold mb-1 text-slate-900">Updates</div>
        <div class="text-slate-600">Weekly diff + 90-day changelog · 360 days included · renewal CHF 120/year</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">10 entity types covered</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
      <table class="min-w-full text-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-lg">
        <thead class="bg-slate-50">
          <tr class="text-left">
            <th class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-slate-200">Entity type</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-slate-200">FINMA list</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Banks</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">Full banking licences + cantonal + private</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Insurance</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">Life + non-life + reinsurance + health</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Payment institutions</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">PSPs, e-money, fintech licences</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Asset managers collective</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">Fund managers under LPCC/CISA</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Asset managers individual</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">LEFin/FinIA authorised</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Securities firms</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">Brokers, market makers</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Fund representatives</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">Foreign fund distribution in CH</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">SRO members</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">Directly subject financial intermediaries (DSFI)</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Supervisory organisations</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">FINSA-supervisor bodies</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Insurance intermediaries</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">Brokers &amp; agents registered with FINMA</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Unified schema across all 10 lists</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
      <table class="min-w-full text-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-lg">
        <thead class="bg-slate-50">
          <tr class="text-left">
            <th class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-slate-200">Field</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-slate-200">Type</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-slate-200">Example</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">entity_type</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">enum (10 values)</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">bank</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">name</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">string</td><td class="px-4 py-2">UBS Switzerland AG</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">uid</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">string (CHE format)</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">CHE-101.329.561</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">lei</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">string (20 chars)</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">506700LOLO53LDMTHY00</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">licence_type</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">string</td><td class="px-4 py-2">fintech licence</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">licence_date</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">string (ISO date)</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">2019-08-27</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">status</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">string</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">active</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">canton</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">string (2-letter)</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">ZH</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">address</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">string</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Bahnhofstrasse 45, 8001 Zürich</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">source_list</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-slate-600">string</td><td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono">finma-banks</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-10">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Free sample — 15 rows across 4 entity types</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-3">Try before you buy. Representative sample: banks, PSPs, insurance, asset managers.</p>
      <a href="/samples/finma-sample.csv" download class="text-indigo-600 font-medium hover:underline">↓ Download finma-sample.csv</a>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Who is this for?</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-700 mb-8">
      <li><strong>Compliance &amp; KYC teams</strong> — onboard counterparties against the unified registry</li>
      <li><strong>Fintechs &amp; PSPs</strong> — verify partner licensing before integration</li>
      <li><strong>Law firms (regulatory)</strong> — due diligence on Swiss financial entities</li>
      <li><strong>Data teams at banks/insurers</strong> — contraparty portfolio audits</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">PSD3 + FinSA 2026-2027 tailwind</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-8">
      With PSD3 tightening counterparty due-diligence across Europe and Swiss FinSA continuing to expand its scope, compliance teams need reliable, machine-readable registries. FINMA publishes the data, but fragmented across 10 different XLSX files with inconsistent schemas. We unify them. Hand-assembly costs 20-30 hours of engineering time per quarter. <strong>CHF 299 once, updated weekly.</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="border-t border-slate-200 pt-10 mt-10 text-center">
      <a href={STRIPE_CHECKOUT_URL} class="inline-block px-10 py-4 rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white text-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
        Buy FINMA Registry — CHF 299
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3">Secure checkout via Stripe · Instant download by email · 14-day refund if not downloaded</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-6">
        Or get all 3 datasets (TARES + Classifications + FINMA) in the <a href="/bundle" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline font-medium">full bundle for CHF 799</a> and save CHF 200.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
